restRequest

public static java.lang.String restRequest(java.lang.String id,
                                           java.lang.String secretKey,
                                           boolean sandbox,
                                           java.lang.String operation,
                                           java.lang.String... paramsList)
                                    throws java.lang.Exception
Performs a REST request on MTurk. The paramsList must be a sequence of strings of the form a1, b1, a2, b2, a3, b3 ... Where aN is a parameter name, and bN is the value for that parameter. Most common parameters have suitable default values, namely: Version, Timestamp, Query, and Signature.

Throws:
java.lang.Exception
